elements.name: How to charge_One Charge including bed and meals - Meals on arrival and departure day_Full charge independent of arrival and departure time

steps.name: open Vessel Manager login with valid user credentials
go to Personnel menu
access Meals and Accommodation sub menu
validate if the current url is correct
input valid date range period and click on submit button
access Setup Meals and Charges page
under How to charge click One Charge including bed and meals radio button
under Meals on day of arrival: click Full charge independent of arrival time radio button
under Meals on departure day: click Full charge independent of departure time radio button
click on save changes button
validate if the confirmation message that the changes has been saved did display
browser will close
